        "title": "Ceramics for Gatherings",
        "text": "<p>UMBRA is closely linked to food and the act of sharing a meal. The pieces are conceived as quiet companions to food, designed to frame dishes without overshadowing them. These pieces are not seen as decorative objects, but as tools that support gestures, textures, and moments at the table. The project is particularly interested in how handmade tableware can influence the experience of eating.</p>"
      }
