        "indent_content": true,
        "title": "About Umbra",
        "text": "<p>UMBRA is a ceramic project founded ten years ago by Alicia Garcia, developed alongside an ongoing architectural practice. It originated in Madrid, but after some changes in life and studio, it is now settled in Luxembourg. Working with clay emerged as a natural extension of an interest in space, proportion, and the everyday objects that shape our routines. Ceramics became a slower, more tactile way of thinking and making highlighting food and the gatherings that take place around a table.</p>"
      }
    },
    "beconcept_numbered_text_mPLieH": {
      "type": "beconcept-numbered-text",
