        "show_number": true,
        "number": 3,
        "indent_content": true,
        "title": "Atelier",
        "text": "<p>All pieces are handmade in a small personal workshop in Luxembourg, where the entire process takes place, from throwing and trimming to glazing and firing. Working on a small scale allows care, flexibility, and attention to each object. The production embraces variation, imperfection, and the traces of the hand, resulting in unique pieces meant to be used, lived with  and integrated into daily life.</p>"
      }
    },
