        "indent_content": true,
        "title": "Notes",
        "text": "<p>UMBRA offers a small selection of pieces through its online shop, available for direct purchase. Alongside this, the studio is open to custom commissions and specific projects, including tableware developed for restaurants, private clients, or particular contexts. Each collaboration is approached as a dialogue, allowing the work to adapt to different needs while staying true to the values of the practice. Feel free to get in touch if you have a project in mind.</p>"
